      "content": "That makes sense. I guess I'm mostly concerned about the \"barrier\" aspect. If we're marketing these as high-end, ultra-dense sheets, shouldn't the weave be tight enough to act as a shield against external contaminants? I want to make sure the weave is effectively \"sealed\" enough so nothing can get through the gaps in the fibers.",
